1
00:00:00,670 --> 00:00:03,752
Mala Goldbaum, film numer akht.

2
00:00:06,340 --> 00:00:08,834
ver iz oyf der fotografye?

3
00:00:08,834 --> 00:00:11,950
mayn Suzan. Suzan, mayn tokhter.

4
00:00:12,021 --> 00:00:14,591
ven hot men aroysgenumen di fotografye?

5
00:00:14,041 --> 00:00:21,402
in tsvey un fertsikstn yor. in der shule, di letste di letste mol vos m'hot zey aroysgevorfn fun der shule.

6
00:00:21,696 --> 00:00:23,560
in tsvey un fertsikstn yor.

7
00:00:23,456 --> 00:00:24,806
in velkhn land?

8
00:00:24,716 --> 00:00:26,506
in Frankraykh.

9
00:00:28,024 --> 00:00:33,688
Alberto oykhet. b- Lazarl nisht. un Zhak oykh nisht.

10
00:00:34,858 --> 00:00:37,113
ver iz oyf der fotografye?

11
00:00:37,474 --> 00:00:42,075
im oykhet in tsvey fertsik oykhet. di zelbe tsayt, zelbe tsayt.

12
00:00:39,533 --> 00:00:40,691
ver iz er?

13
00:00:42,216 --> 00:00:43,520
in der shule.

14
00:00:43,360 --> 00:00:44,380
ver iz er?

15
00:00:45,080 --> 00:00:46,260
vi heyst er?

16
00:00:46,120 --> 00:00:51,949
Alberto. Alberto, in der zelber tsayt hot men im fotografirt un im.

17
00:00:51,949 --> 00:00:53,583
un Zhakn shoyn nisht,

18
00:00:53,623 --> 00:00:55,640
un im un im oykh nisht.

19
00:00:55,640 --> 00:00:57,228
vi alt iz er geven?

20
00:00:57,370 --> 00:01:02,189
er iz alt geven efsher iz er nayn yor. nayn yor.

21
00:01:02,860 --> 00:01:05,940
in velkher shule hot men im aroysgenumen?

22
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:05,969
in Frankraykh.

23
00:01:09,604 --> 00:01:11,775
ver iz oyf der fotografye?

24
00:01:11,933 --> 00:01:15,015
dos iz Malaz U.

25
00:01:15,358 --> 00:01:23,435
fun iz men gekumen fun Afrike mentshn, zey hobn aroysgenumen di kinder fun der shif, un di goyim

26
00:01:23,577 --> 00:01:27,148
a por hundert kinder, di vos hobn nisht keyn tate mit a mame.

27
00:01:27,154 --> 00:01:32,463
hobn zey im oykh gezen, hobn zey fotografirt mir un zey hobn im gevolt koyfn bay mir.

28
00:01:32,554 --> 00:01:39,348
hob ikh nisht gevolt. hob ikh nisht gevolt gebn. hob ikh do dem foto UNK kind oykhet.

29
00:01:39,490 --> 00:01:46,841
zey hobn mir gemakht a foto far mir, un tsunemen dos kind. zog ikh, neyn. dos kind geb ikh nisht avek.

30
00:01:47,269 --> 00:01:51,431
velkhe mame get avek a kind? keyner nisht.

31
00:01:54,812 --> 00:01:57,405
ver gefint zikh oyf der fotografye?

32
00:01:57,411 --> 00:02:07,549
dos iz mayn, ikh shtey, un mayn zun shteyt, un ver iz der driter?

33
00:02:07,528 --> 00:02:12,708
di tokhter. di tokhter.

34
00:02:13,189 --> 00:02:15,327
Suzan. Suzan.

35
00:02:15,262 --> 00:02:17,819
zogt mir di nemen fun ale dray.

36
00:02:17,737 --> 00:02:19,655
ikh bin di mame fun ale.

37
00:02:19,327 --> 00:02:21,196
yo, zogt mir dem nomen.

38
00:02:21,196 --> 00:02:28,033
Suzan un Zhak un ikh. Male.

39
00:02:26,738 --> 00:02:28,033
vi heyst ir?

40
00:02:28,883 --> 00:02:30,024
Male.

41
00:02:35,582 --> 00:02:38,073
ver shteyt oyf der fotografye?

42
00:02:38,738 --> 00:02:57,057
ikh Male, Suzan, no, Suzan nisht. Male, Suzan oykhet, Suzan, Debi, un m- Leser, Misher.

43
00:03:03,595 --> 00:03:06,491
ven hot men aroysgenumen di fotografye?

44
00:03:06,683 --> 00:03:09,933
ikh veys nisht, az nisht zog ikh aykh. shoyn a yor.

45
00:03:09,990 --> 00:03:12,498
ver ver hot khasene gehat do?

46
00:03:12,589 --> 00:03:14,262
mayn tokhter's zun.

47
00:03:14,188 --> 00:03:15,106
vi heyst er?

48
00:03:15,221 --> 00:03:15,925
Riki.

49
00:03:15,925 --> 00:03:18,405
ver nokh shteyt oyf der fotografye?

50
00:03:18,512 --> 00:03:28,411
Riki, iz Golde, Marek, S- un Debi. un s'vayb veys ikh nisht vi zi heyst.

51
00:03:28,485 --> 00:03:30,279
un ayer tokhter oykhet?

52
00:03:31,028 --> 00:03:33,454
ayer tokhter shteyt oyf der fotografye?

53
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:35,887
yo, mayn tokhter shteyt oyf dem.

54
00:03:34,716 --> 00:03:35,847
vi heyst zi?

55
00:03:35,927 --> 00:03:37,119
Suzan.

56
00:03:41,310 --> 00:03:44,257
ver gefint zikh oyf di fotografye?

57
00:03:45,023 --> 00:03:48,122
mayne kinder. Zhak,

58
00:03:52,836 --> 00:03:55,175
di andere zaynen di eyniklekh?

59
00:03:55,924 --> 00:04:02,918
neyn. s'do mayn shnur, ikh ze nisht azoy vayt UNK.

60
00:04:02,286 --> 00:04:05,590
vi heysn di Zhak's kinder?

61
00:04:05,573 --> 00:04:12,607
Zhak's kinder heyst m- Pavelo, Dzhego, Lili, Maryele.

62
00:04:16,274 --> 00:04:20,622
ver shteyt oyf der fotografye? ver iz oyf der fotografye?

63
00:04:20,344 --> 00:04:32,874
mayn zun Zha- Abe, un zayn vayb Malke, un Ma- un ikh Male, un beyde kinderlekh. vi zey heysn veys ikh nisht.

64
00:04:33,133 --> 00:04:36,805
zey zaynen ayer zun's eyniklekh?

65
00:04:36,825 --> 00:04:38,754
dos iz tsvey ur-eyniklekh.

66
00:04:38,764 --> 00:04:40,288
ayere ur-eyniklekh.

67
00:04:40,223 --> 00:04:42,124
ur-eyniklekh, yo.

68
00:04:44,710 --> 00:04:48,011
dertseylt mir ver shteyt oyf der fotografye?

69
00:04:48,152 --> 00:05:16,684
dortn? shteyt der ershter veys ikh nisht. Margerita dakht zikh mir, hintn iz Albert, Zhak, un un oykh un oykh,

70
00:05:16,671 --> 00:05:19,458
der anderer zun, vi heyst er?

71
00:05:19,401 --> 00:05:33,534
Leon, Leon, un un Marge- Kler Ma- Ma- UNK Malke.

72
00:05:33,534 --> 00:05:37,961
Maryela. Maryela.

73
00:05:37,459 --> 00:05:48,677
Maryela, Maryela, un Lili. un ikh, ikh Male. ikh hob shoyn gezogt, male. shoyn.

74
00:05:49,915 --> 00:05:51,900
ver shteyt mit aykh?

75
00:05:52,227 --> 00:06:01,468
Alberto Goldbaum, Mala Goldbaum. Alberto Goldbaum, Zhak Goldbaum, Margarita Goldbaum.

